 Hello,


 Be a part of your first get together as alumni, immediately after you
 become one! I&AR Team brings you AlumNite 2016, an evening with your
 friends and family.


 Alike last year, this year's program is being designed like an Awards
 show, with presentations interwoven with music, singing and more fun
 performances by the students.


 Date: July 23rd
 Time: 4:30 PM
 Venue: CLT


 Main activities of the evening


     Acts staged by the Class of '16!
     Launch of an Institute Chair
     Conferral of "Distinguished Alumnus Awards" on three of our DAs
    for this year
     Awarding of several alumnifunded prizes for students & faculty.
     A show by Raftar, our very own Formula Racing Car team
     Timeonstage for reps of last year's reunion batches.
     Dinner!


 The evening will begin with tea and end with dinner. Mark your calendar,
 come with family, and have a great time! Please head to the FB Event Page
  to stay updated with
 the developments!


 Please note that due to space limitations, we have only 300 spots
 available for the Batch of 2016, including their guests. Please RSVP to 

  to confirm your
 attendance.


